https://github.com/ronilaukkarinen/weed

1. backup .irssi/
2. git clone https://github.com/ronilaukkarinen/weed.git weed-master
3. weed-master/weed.theme, weed-master/scripts/* ::

    cp ~/weed-master/weed.theme ~/.irssi/
    mkdir -p ~/.irssi/scripts && cp ~/weed-master/scripts/* ~/.irssi/scripts/

4. config

    cp ~/weed-master/config ~/.irssi/
    # add self infomation

5. irssi reload

    [in irssi] /reload

6. More feature

    /script load awl
    /script load usercount.pl
        /sbar awl_0 add -before awl_0 -alignment left usercount
    /script load nicklist
        /nicklist screen
